-block-content stk-content-align stk-d9d5efb-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-853ce3c\" data-block-id=\"853ce3c\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-853ce3c-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-853ce3c-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-853ce3c-inner-blocks\">\n<p>If you are still wondering if Halong is the place to hold your dream destination wedding, we can guarantee it is the perfect place for an one-of-a-kind celebration of love. A charming coastal city whose resume speaks for itself: a UNESCO World Heritage Site, Vietnam&#8217;s top tourism center and a proven choice for couples all around the world.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>See more reasons why this city is an ideal destination to hold your wedding: <a href=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/halong-and-6-reasons-to-hold-your-wedding-here\/\">6 great reasons to hold your wedding in Halong<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" data-id=\"17210\" src=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Ha_Long_2019_taken_by_DJI_FC220.jpeg\" alt=\"-\" class=\"wp-image-17210\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Ha_Long_2019_taken_by_DJI_FC220.jpeg 2000w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Ha_Long_2019_taken_by_DJI_FC220-768x512.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/theplannersvn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Ha_Long_2019_taken_by_DJI_FC220-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns stk-block-columns stk-block stk-05f1372\" data-block-id=\"05f1372\"><style>.stk-05f1372{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0% !important}@media screen and (max-width:1024px){.stk-05f1372{padding-top:3em !important;padding-right:3em !important;padding-bottom:3em !important;padding-left:3em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}@media screen and (max-width:767px){.stk-05f1372{padding-top:0em !important;padding-right:0em !important;padding-bottom:0em !important;padding-left:0em !important;margin-bottom:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-05f1372-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-block-column--v2 stk-column stk-block stk-66ec7ce\" data-block-id=\"66ec7ce\"><style>@media screen and (max-width:1025px){.stk-66ec7ce-container{margin-top:20px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-bottom:20px !important;margin-left:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-66ec7ce-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-66ec7ce-inner-blocks\">\n<p>Located in Quang Ninh Province in Northern Vietnam, Halong City is famous for its hospitable peoples, flavorful cuisine, pleasant weather, tropical paradise landscape and the worldly renowned Halong Bay &#8211; recognized as a World&#8217;s Natural Heritage Site. The Bay, consisting of thousands of limestone karsts and isles in numerous shapes and sizes, has become a rising destination for couples to celebrate their weddings in recent years. Shall we review some prominent venues for a wedding of your dream?<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-